HOW IT STARTED

Neuko's lore centers on a cryptic conspiracy involving psychic experiments, a mysterious character known as G*Boy (G304), and the fictional MITER-Corp.

What began as experiments on "homeless babies" to create psychic soldiers evolved into a story of escape, rebellion, and a decentralized network of "operatives" — you.
